<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169461>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Helicopsyche sucrensis, new species, holotype. 1 — sternum VI process, lateral; 2 — sternum VI process, ventral; 3 — male genitalia, lateral; 4 — male genitalia, dorsal; 5 — male genitalia, ventral; 6 — phallus, lateral; 7 — phallus, ventral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169461/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.169478>
    dc:description "FIGURE 90. Map of Venezuela showing distributions of H. merida (circle), H. laneblina (rectangle), H. sucrensis (cross), H. breviterga (diamond), and H. circulata (triangle)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/169478/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

